{"tid":1727222,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[急]呢場運動急需和理非出嚟show民意","createTime":"2019-11-16T11:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:47:45.000Z","uid":7692,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"64e073e3c1947a9ddd52b0d7662e8c3cc1717f5f","tid":1727222,"uid":7692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"最好就係聽日<br />\n再遲下個禮拜黎明行動會好有壓力<br />\n咁急遊行集會都搞唔到<br />\n召集十八區係自己商場召集唱榮光同嗌口號係最易！<br />\n當個個場都坐爆政府仲有咩籍口？<br />\n而且可以穩軍心<br />\n打擊返藍絲<br />\n要好似出反蒙面法個日咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1qKO5w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1qKO5w.png&h=2b6fdee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支持嘅幫手推推比文宣見到"},{"pid":"c28bc5e3e135b426753524d16b15de2c1bfeede3","tid":1727222,"uid":252004,"like":1,"dislike":38,"score":-37,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"718487144dd31e206661fdf5fbcb14af2e6dcc62","tid":1727222,"uid":92188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:12:33.000Z","msg":"聽晚有個夜晚集會，大家宣傳下"},{"pid":"346c811ceef960f63efd8db997066615422feac1","tid":1727222,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:13:12.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=32390806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=7c2ddd93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"f24f8962745139e2b3484a66c5ec8bfb5653494f","tid":1727222,"uid":44298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:13:20.000Z","msg":"如果可以嘅我想遊埋行添"},{"pid":"181feec16cd2684f9f9b3100435cacb33f91e9a7","tid":1727222,"uid":28905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:13:21.000Z","msg":"又分勇武和理非"},{"pid":"741848fa1ded1b64480f55b395b2fbebc06ab2a5","tid":1727222,"uid":43113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fd383912ff47012a80da390d570f81f9dd98d8f","tid":1727222,"uid":43113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa5b38ab2c2ae9e9386d0d1d24cf03670ad79064","tid":1727222,"uid":43113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:13:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ec58da3004fcd95332f23f519974c6df4190eaa","tid":1727222,"uid":43113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:14:03.